<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        .email-card {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: auto;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .section-title {
            color: #007bff;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .details { line-height: 1.6; }
        .footer { font-size: 12px; color: #888; margin-top: 30px; text-align: center; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-card">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Booking Confirmed!</h2>
        </div>
        
        <div class="details">
            <p>Hello <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>
            <p>Your ride request (ID: #{{bookingId}}) has been successfully processed and a driver has been allotted.</p>

            <h3 class="section-title">Driver & Vehicle</h3>
            <p><strong>Driver Name:</strong> {{driverName}}</p>
            <p><strong>Driver PhoneNumber:</strong>{{driverPhoneNumber}}</p>
            <p><strong>Car Model:</strong> {{carModel}}</p>

            <h3 class="section-title">Trip Details</h3>
            <p><strong>From:</strong> {{pickup}}</p>
            <p><strong>To:</strong> {{drop}}</p>
            <p><strong>Total Fare:</strong> â‚¹{{fare}}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thank you for choosing Carisma Car Rentals.</p>
            <p>If you have any questions, contact us at support@carisma.com</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>